fic work under the HIV/AIDS Response Project. Additionally, the WB is very supportive of CS engagement in health sector activities, such as participation in JANS and development partner fora, etc. For more information, please see tab 8DP and relevant sources noted therein.'),(6074,292,'21','2005','0.0','2009','0.0','All World Bank disbursements given to the Government of Mozambique.'),(6075,292,'22','2005','','2009','0.0','During CY05, approximately 50% of disbursements to the health sector were under the Mozambique PRSC - by which the WB provides funds directly to the Government Treasury. However, outside of the PRSC, WB funding was not provided via general budget support, but rather, it provided investment lending.'),(6076,292,'23','2005','0.0','2009','0.0','WB funding was not provided via general budget support, but rather, it provided investment lending.'),(6077,293,'1','2005','No','2009','Yes','Please note: There was no existing country compact during baseline year 2005.'),(6078,293,'2','2005','4900000.0','2009','16400000.0','For a detailed record of disbursements for calendar years 2005 and 2009 please see excel tab 2DPa, which breaks down monthly disbursements for all active projects during these calendar years.'),(6079,293,'3','','4900000.0','','16400000.0','The WB disburses directly to the Government of Nepal.'),(6080,293,'4','2005','0.0','2009','0.0','In accordance with agreed division of labor, the United Kingdom DfID finances technical cooperation for the Health Sector Program.'),(6081,293,'5','','0.0','','0.0','While DfID provides support for technical cooperation it is important to note that WB support to the health sector is fully coordinated with other partners and in line with the national health strategy. Please see tab 2DPb for more information.'),(6082,293,'6','2005','4900000.0','2009','16400000.0','Please note that totals given for \"health sector aid for the government sector ($USD)\" (2DPa-2) and \"health sector aid ($USD) did you disburse at 