e.','','',''),(12,9,2,'Une approche sectorielle et un mcanisme relatif au fonds commun taient en place en 2007 et un accord IHP+ a t sign en 2008.','','','','','','Cette mesure de la performance standard est tire des donnes recueillies dans le cadre du suivi de lenqute de Paris de lOCDE-CAD. Lvaluation approprie na pas t ralise au Mozambique.','','',''),(13,10,1,'An agreement was signed in 2005 called the \'Cadre de Partenariat entre le Ministere de la Sante Publique et de la lutte contre les endemies et les Parternaires Techniques et Financiers pour la mise en oeuvre du PNDS 2005-2009\' ','','','','','','In 2007, Niger scored a B in the 4 point evaluation scale. No comparable evaluation took place to enable a rating.','','',''),(14,10,2,'The \'Cadre de Partenariat entre le Ministere de la Sante Publique et de la lutte contre les endemies et les Parternaires Techniques et Financiers pour la mise en oeuvre du PNDS 2005-2009\' was signed in 2005.','','','','','','En 2007, le Niger a obtenu B  l\'chelle d\'valuation  quatre points. Aucune valuation comparable n\'a t effectue pour permettre une valuation.','','',''),(15,11,1,'In 2009 there was evidence of a Compact under development, and in December 2010 this was signed and in place.','','','','','','This Standard Performance Measure uses data from the OECD/DAC Paris Survey monitoring. The relevant assessment was not completed in Nigeria.','','Mutual assessments were not undertaken in 2009, however in 2010 mutual assessment started with the JAR. ',''),(16,11,2,'Le Nigeria a labor un accord IHP+ qui a t sign le 16 dcembre 2010.','','','','','','Cette mesure de la performance standard est tire des donnes recueillies dans le cadre du suivi de lenqute de Paris de lOCDE-CAD. Lvaluation approprie na pas t ralise au Nigeria.','','',''),(17,3,1,'A Memorandum of Understanding was signed in 2008, which is currently being implemented.','','','','','','This Standard Performance Measure uses data from the OECD/DAC Paris Survey monitoring. The relevant assessment was not completed in Burundi.','','',''),(18,3,2,'Il existe un Memorandum Of Understanding( MOU) qui date de fvrier 2008.Il est en train d\'tre mis en uvre.','','','','','','Cette mesure de la performance standard est tire des donnes recueillies dans le cadre du suivi de lenqute de Paris de lOCDE-CAD. Lvaluation approprie na pas t ralise au Burundi.','','',''),(19,5,1,'There is evidence of a Compact or equivalent agreement under development. The aim is to have this in place during 2011.','','','','','','This Standard Performance Measure uses data from the OECD/DAC Paris Survey monitoring. The relevant assessment was not completed in Djibouti.','','',''),(20,5,2,'Le processus d\'laboration du compact pays est en cours et le compact sera probalement sign en frvrier 2011.','','','','','','Cette mesure de la performance standard est tire des donnes recueillies dans le cadre du suivi de lenqute de Paris de lOCDE-CAD. Lvaluation approprie na pas t ralise a Djibouti. ','','','');
